data.description: Look no further for the perfect home. This beautiful newly renovated 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths features updated hardwood floors throughout the first floor, brand new kitchen with new cabinets, and quartz counter tops. New appliances including a Samsung 5 burner Wifi stove, microwave oven, and dish washer. New windows through most of the house, new carpeting in the first floor bedroom and throughout the 2nd floor, new roof, new HVAC system with a Google Nest Wifi thermostat, newly renovated 2nd floor bathroom, and master bathroom has been renovated from original design. And master bedroom has its own private deck overlooking the pool.The private backyard is a canvas for your outdoor dreams, whether it's gardening, entertaining on the screened in back porch, or simply enjoying the gorgeous 25ft salt water gunite pool that has been resurfaced with new equipment. One of the standout features of this property is the spacious unfinished basement. It presents a world of possibilities, whether you envision it as a workshop, home gym, entertainment area, or additional living space. Easy access to Hwy 78 and 124. Also minutes from Hwy 285. This property is located in an established neighborhood with no HOA.   This property is ready to welcome you home to Snellville Georgia!
